extends layout

block content
  // About page intro
  section.about-section
    h1 About Us

    // Small story
    p Downtown Donuts has been family-owned since 1992, serving fresh donuts, coffee, and breakfast favorites to the downtown community.
    p What started as a small neighborhood spot has grown into a local favorite, known for quality ingredients and a welcoming atmosphere.
    p Whether you're stopping by for your morning coffee or grabbing a quick bite, our goal is to make every visit simple, fresh, and enjoyable.

  
  // Info cards
  section.info-grid
    .info-card
      h2 Since 1992
      p A long-time local favorite with a warm neighborhood feel.

    .info-card
      h2 Fresh Daily
      p Donuts and coffee made fresh every morning.

    .info-card
      h2 Order Online
      p Easy links for customers to order through delivery services.